Stratos Framework is a framework for executes webbots. It's a way for write faster and easyly webbots inside a context which provide the common webbots operations.
This is the first stable version. In short future I will upload a set of webbot samples running over the framewrok. The framework was develop as an aid during the
 construcction of webbot for comercial purposes in cuba which has not released yet. For this reason the first commit has not a context to be tested, but for  those
 with souls of entrepeneurs I'll give you a hint: Extend the lib/scraper/Webbot.class.php in the bot directory and check the script/launcher.php.


